{"tid":472214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冷鋒殺到周末急降6度 下禮拜低見16℃","createTime":"2017-11-18T04:21:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T15:47:18.000Z","uid":41423,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"e588be603c6c4df344348b8260c3303cb876acdc","tid":472214,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:21:43.000Z","msg":"一道冷鋒今日將抵達華南沿岸，隨後的強烈東北季候風會為本港帶來顯著較涼的天氣。天文台預計，市區氣溫會由今日最高的25&deg;C，顯著下降至明日清晨最低的18&deg;C，下周二更進一步跌至16&deg;C，而預料該東北季候風在下周會持續影響華南，本港將繼續清涼，下周後期兩日最低氣溫亦見16&deg;C，較日前的預測為低。<br />\n<br />\n天色方面，隨著冷鋒今日壓境，天文台料本港今日將由早上部分時間有陽光，能見度較低，中午過後轉為有幾陣雨；明日密雲及有幾陣微雨；下周一繼續多雲，至下周二才短暫時間有陽光。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171118/20218471\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171118%2F20218471&d=LokDDrC3299haMjCSi6EvP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=2241c327\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171118%2F20218471&h=04bb3ad3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171118/20218471</a>"},{"pid":"aafe6ce344309ae791b9f437e8042f46752b3327","tid":472214,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:25:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b41832ab3f6995a0a516cc5c455ca3428a13d0a2","tid":472214,"uid":132038,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:26:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0deffaea619bbfeae64145d1543c95b6b2e75f94","tid":472214,"uid":71092,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:27:21.000Z","msg":"真係凍先好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"620eac82601f2c6bf0df07a01322d5b7ac9444a7","tid":472214,"uid":132587,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:28:18.000Z","msg":"日本宜家8度 韓國1度<br />\n香港琴日29度<img src=\"/as